description:
Kate enjoys the simple things that bring her pleasure and Doree reveals that she’s drinking coffee again. Then, Be There In Five Podcast host, author, and entrepreneur Kate Kennedy joins Forever35 to talk about how she walks the line of being both a critic and a participant of internet culture, what it’s like being an HSP in the limelight, and why she’s an unapologetic stan of Taylor Swift.


To leave a voicemail or text for a future episode, reach us at 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.

Visit forever35podcast.com for links to everything we mention on the show.

Follow us on Twitter (@Forever35Pod) and Instagram (@Forever35Podcast) and join the Forever35 Facebook Group (Password: Serums).
